<lg> <tl> <note type="source" target="#right(408)">SSP 5.64cd 5.65ab: samyag ānandajanakaḥ sadguruḥ so 'bhidhīyate | nimiṣārdhārdhapātād vā yad vā pādāvalokanāt |</note><anchor xml:id="408"/><note type="testium" target="#right(409)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: nimeṣārddhena tasyaiva ājñāpālanato bhavet | mahānandaśataprāptis tasmai śrīgurave namaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="409"/>samyag ānanda<app><lem wit="#B #E #L #P #U2">jananaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">jananaṃ</rdg></app> sadguruḥ sobhidhīyate/</tl> <tl> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">nimeṣārddhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#P #N2">nimiṣārddhaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">nimeṣārddhā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vā</lem><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">ca</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E #P #U2">tatpādaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">tatpāda</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">pādaṃ vā</rdg></app> yad vākyād avalokanāt//4 //</tl> </lg><lg> <tl> <note type="source" target="#right(410)">SSP 5.65cd 5.66ab: svātmānaṃ sthiram ādhatte tasmai śrīgurave namaḥ | nānāvikalpaviśrāntiṃ kathayā kurute tu yaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="410"/><note type="testium" target="#right(411)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: nānāvikalpavibhrāntināśañca kurute tu yaḥ | sadguruḥ sa tu vijñeyo na tu vairaprakalpakaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="411"/>svātmā sthiratvam āyāti tasmai <app><lem wit="#ceteri">śrīgurave</lem><rdg wit="#L">śrīgurubho</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">śrīguru namo</rdg></app> namaḥ/</tl> <tl> <app><lem wit="#N1 #U2">nānāvikalpaviśrāntiṃ</lem><rdg wit="#D">nānāvikalpaṃ viśrāṃtiṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#E">nānāviplavaviśrāntiḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#P">nānāvikalpaḥ viśrāṃtiḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">nānāvikalpaviśrāṃti</rdg><rdg wit="#N2">nānāvikalpaviśrāṃti</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">kathanāt ku</lem><rdg wit="#B">kathanāt |</rdg></app>rute <app><lem wit="#B #L #P #U2">tu yaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#E">tataḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">tu saḥ</rdg></app>/</tl> <tl> <note type="source" target="#right(410)">SSP 5.66cd: sadguruḥ sa tu vijñeyo na tu mithyāviḍambakaḥ||5.67||</note><anchor xml:id="410"/>sadguruḥ sa tu <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vijñeyo</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">vijño</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">na tu</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">nnu</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vipriyajalpakaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">viprāyajalākaḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#E">vai priyajalpakaḥ</rdg></app>//5 //</tl> </lg><p> <note type="source" target="#right(411)">SSP 5.67: ata eva paramapadaprāpty arthaṃ sa sadguruḥ sadā vandanīyaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="411"/><note type="testium" target="#right(412)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: ata eva maheśāni sadguruḥ śiva āditaḥ | satyavādī ca sacchīlo gurubhakto dṛḍhavrataḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="412"/>ata eva <app><lem wit="#ceteri">paramapadaprāpty a</lem><rdg wit="#E #P">paramapadasya prāpty</rdg></app>arthaṃ sadguruḥ <app><lem wit="#D #N1 #N2">sarvadā vandyaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#E #P #U2">sevyaḥ sarvadā</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">sevyasarvadā</rdg></app>/ yaḥ puruṣaḥ satyavādī bhavati/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">nirantaraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#P">niraṃtara°</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">gurusevā</lem><rdg wit="#U2">gusevā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">rato</lem><rdg wit="#B">taro</rdg><rdg wit="#E">tatparo</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhavati</lem><rdg wit="#D">bhava</rdg></app>/ yasya manasi <app><lem wit="#ceteri">pāpaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">pāpa</rdg></app> na bhavati/ <note type="source" target="#right(413)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: svalpācāraratātmā yo dānādiśīlasaṃyutaḥ | kāpaṭyalobhavinyāsau mahāvaṃśasamudbhavaḥ |</note><anchor xml:id="413"/><app><lem wit="#E #P">svācārarataḥ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">svācāraratāḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">svācārataḥ ||</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">svasyācārarato</rdg></app> snānādiśīlo bhavati/ kāpaṭyaṃ <app><lem wit="#E #P #L #U2">na bhavati</lem><rdg wit="#B">bhavati</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">nāsti</rdg></app>/ yasya <app><lem wit="#ceteri">vaṃśaparaṃparā</lem><rdg wit="#D">parāparaṃparā</rdg></app> jñāyate/ <note type="source" target="#right(414)">Ysv<hi rend="sup">PT</hi>: īdṛśaḥ sadgurustasya saṅgatau yatnavān bhavet | tad eva manasaḥ śāntiṃ prāpnoti paramaṃ padam |</note><anchor xml:id="414"/>etādṛśasya <app><lem wit="#ceteri">sadguroḥ</lem><rdg wit="#U2">guroḥ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E #D #N1 #U2">saṃgatiḥ</lem><rdg wit="#P #N2">saṃgati</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">saṃgatī</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#B #E #L #P #U2">karttavyā</lem><rdg wit="#D #N1">kattavyāḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#N2">karttavyāḥ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E">tena</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">om.</rdg></app> puruṣasya <app><lem wit="#ceteri">manaḥ</lem><rdg wit="#U2">mano</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">śāntiṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">śāṃti</rdg></app> prāpnoti/ atha ca <app><lem wit="#ceteri">yasya</lem><rdg wit="#U2">om.</rdg></app> manomadhye <app><lem wit="#E #D #N1 #N2">sthira</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">sīraḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#P">sira</rdg><rdg wit="#N2">sthīrā°</rdg></app>ānanda utpadyate/ so 'pi sadguruḥ kathyate/ <note type="philcomm" target="#right(415)">E omits this sentence.</note><anchor xml:id="415"/>atha <app><lem wit="#ceteri">ca</lem><rdg wit="#U2">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem resp="#ego" type="emendation">ghaṭimātraṃ</lem><rdg wit="#N2">em. ghaṭimātra°</rdg><rdg wit="#D">ghaṭīṃ mātraṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#N1">ghaṭī....mo</rdg><rdg wit="#ceteri">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#B #L #P #N1 #D">ghaṭikārdhaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#N2">°ghaṃṭikārddhaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">ghaṭikā</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#L #N2 #U2">ghaṭikā</lem><rdg wit="#N1 #D">ghaṭikāyāḥ</rdg><rdg wit="#B #P">ghaṃṭikā°</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#B #P #L #U2">caturthāṃśo</lem><rdg wit="#N1">caturtho ḍaṃśo</rdg><rdg wit="#N2">caturtho daṃśo</rdg><rdg wit="#D">caturtho aṃśo</rdg></app> vā yasya pārśvaṃ upaviṣṭe satyatādṛṣo bhāvo manomadhye <app><lem wit="#ceteri">utpadyate</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">uppapadyate</rdg></app>/ </p>
